    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >死后，你的灵魂进入了永恒流浪的炼狱。唯一的出路是击败守卫自由之门的大恶魔。穿越不安的灵魂、恐怖的怪物和恶魔的群体战斗。收集倒下敌人的灵魂并用它们改变你的外貌。你可以扮演任何被你击败的角色。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843650/extras/2d84ce502fa50b3b199530cd090e8fed.poster.avif?t=1770505242\" width=640 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843650/extras/2d84ce502fa50b3b199530cd090e8fed.webm?t=1770505242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843650/extras/2d84ce502fa50b3b199530cd090e8fed.mp4?t=1770505242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特点</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>灵魂吞噬者</strong><br>消灭并吸收敌人的灵魂，然后扮演他们。这是一种独特的系统，允许你扮演被击败的角色。拥有大量不同职业和技能的角色，每个角色都有自己的优点和缺点，以及独特的发展路径。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>发展路径</strong><br>提升你的角色等级。每个等级可能增加或减少某些属性。用神器和星石强化你的角色。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>职业</strong><br>游戏中有多种不同的职业。每个职业都有自己独特的优势，可以进行培养和发展。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>星图</strong><br>收集星石，通过占星师提升特定职业的属性。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>神器</strong><br>收集散布在炼狱中的各种神器。有些会增强你，而有些会削弱你，有时甚至两者兼具——选择权在你手中。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>首领</strong><br>挑战致命的首领。你甚至可以吸收其中一些的灵魂。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>危险关卡</strong><br>炼狱被分为多个关卡，并非所有关卡都是安全的。一些关卡会对玩家和其他生物施加天气、魔法等效果。只有最坚韧的生物才能存活。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843650/extras/dc80a746adfc82d1856cf3f530f79bd2.poster.avif?t=1770505242\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843650/extras/dc80a746adfc82d1856cf3f530f79bd2.webm?t=1770505242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1843650/extras/dc80a746adfc82d1856cf3f530f79bd2.mp4?t=1770505242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
